sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE as Angular Order Edit UI
    participant API as Catalogs API
    participant UC as GetOrderFormCatalogsUseCase
    participant Cache as ICacheProvider
    participant Slow as SlowCatalogSource

    FE->>API: GET /api/v1/catalogs/order-form
    API->>UC: Request order form catalogs
    UC->>Cache: Get key order-form-catalogs:v1

    alt Cache miss
        Cache-->>UC: No value
        UC->>Slow: Load order statuses and shipping methods
        Note over Slow: Simulated delay around 2 seconds
        Slow-->>UC: Catalog payload
        UC->>Cache: Set key with TTL
        UC-->>API: Catalogs with source slow-source
        API-->>FE: 200 OK, duration around 2000 ms
    else Cache hit
        Cache-->>UC: Cached catalog payload
        UC-->>API: Catalogs with source cache
        API-->>FE: 200 OK, duration under 50 ms
    end

    Note over Cache: PoC adapter uses IMemoryCache
    Note over Cache: Future production adapter can use Redis through the same port
